```
Hero zone: x 0–422   |   Enemy zone: x 422–844
HUD strip: y 310–390  |   Battle area: y 0–310

Formation slot positions (from gameConfig.FORMATION.HERO_POSITIONS):
  Slot 0 Front-Left:  x=280  y=100
  Slot 1 Front-Right: x=280  y=210
  Slot 2 Back-Left:   x=110  y=100
  Slot 3 Back-Right:  x=110  y=210
