## Sequential Build Order — One System at a Time

Work through these 10 prompts in order. Do not skip. Do not combine two prompts into one request.

```
1.  Project scaffold — types, gameConfig, stub scenes, Vite config
2.  BattleScene canvas — 4 hero circles rendered in formation positions
3.  AutoBattleSystem — attack timers, damage, death detection
4.  TargetingSystem — per-class AI target selection
5.  FormationSystem — class-to-position mapping, walk-in animation
6.  UltimateSystem — energy bars, portrait glow, ultimate resolution, auto mode
7.  WaveSystem — 4 waves + Rift Warden boss with telegraph slam
8.  VictoryScene + DefeatScene + complete scene loop
9.  FormationScene — 4-slot grid, hero assignment, save persistence
10. Capacitor Android build — landscape lock, safe area, device test
```

